<h1 class="hero-h">A new AI lead-gen system, deployed at a <em style="color:#00C853;font-style:italic;">Gold's Gym franchise.</em></h1>
<p class="hero-sub">A pioneering AI-driven gym lead-generation deployment at Gold's Gym Newburgh/Middletown. Built through FitCopilot.ai (the AI agent platform Bill co-founded as the productization of the GTM patterns Treetop had been running with fitness clients). 16 unique data points captured per inbound prospect. Generative AI used to recommend specific equipment and program paths for each prospect once in-club. The MVP launch generated 120 qualified leads in a two-week window — and achieved the lowest cost-per-lead in the location's history.</p>
<div class="headline-metric">
<div class="metric-num">Lowest CPL</div>
<div class="metric-label">in Gold's Gym Newburgh/Middletown history — at MVP scale, with the AI lead-gen system live</div>
</div>
<div class="disclosure"><p>Named engagement, published with the consent of the participants. Specific cost-per-lead numbers aggregated for confidentiality; relative comparison ("lowest in location history") reflects the actual operator outcome.</p></div>
</div></div>

